---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro'
import Header from '../components/Header.astro'
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro'
---

<Base title="Terms of Service - Accounting Bridge" description="Terms of Service for Accounting Bridge.">
  <Header />
  <main class="pt-24 pb-20">
    <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 prose prose-gray">
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark mb-2">Terms of Service</h1>
      <p class="text-sm text-muted-light mb-8">Last updated: February 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mt-8 mb-3">1. Service</h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
        Accounting Bridge is a cloud-based financial consolidation and reporting tool operated by
        Wietze Suijker ("we", "us"). By creating an account or using the service, you agree to these terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mt-8 mb-3">2. Accounts</h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
        You are responsible for maintaining the confidentiality of your login credentials.
        One account per person; accounts are non-transferable. We reserve the right to suspend
        accounts that violate these terms.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mt-8 mb-3">3. Subscriptions and payment</h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
        Paid plans are billed monthly. Payments are processed through Stripe. Subscriptions renew
        automatically unless cancelled before the next billing date. Cancellation takes effect at the
        end of the current billing period - no partial refunds. We may change pricing with 30 days notice
        to existing subscribers.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mt-8 mb-3">4. Free tier and demo</h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
        The demo is provided as-is for evaluation purposes. Demo data is shared and may be reset at
        any time. Authenticated free accounts may have feature limitations.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mt-8 mb-3">5. Your data</h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
        You retain ownership of all data you upload or create. We do not claim any intellectual property
        rights over your content. Uploaded files are processed in memory and never stored
        (see our <a href="/privacy" class="text-primary hover:underline">Privacy page</a> for details).
        We store only your configuration, aggregated period summaries, and notes.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mt-8 mb-3">6. Data processing</h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
        By using the service, you authorize us to process your uploaded files for the purpose of
        generating consolidated financial reports. When AI features are enabled, aggregated (non-row-level)
        data may be sent to Anthropic's API. No data is shared with any other third party.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mt-8 mb-3">7. Availability</h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
        We aim for high availability but do not guarantee uninterrupted service. Scheduled maintenance
        will be communicated in advance when possible. We are not liable for losses arising from
        service interruptions.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mt-8 mb-3">8. Limitation of liability</h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
        The service is provided "as is" without warranty of any kind. We are not liable for any indirect,
        incidental, or consequential damages. Our total liability is limited to the amount you have paid us
        in the 12 months preceding the claim. You are responsible for verifying the accuracy of any
        financial output before relying on it.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mt-8 mb-3">9. Termination</h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
        Either party may terminate at any time. On termination, your access ceases at the end of the paid
        billing period. You may export or delete your data before termination. We will delete your data
        within 30 days of account closure upon request.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mt-8 mb-3">10. Changes to these terms</h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
        We may update these terms with 30 days notice via email. Continued use after the notice period
        constitutes acceptance.
      </p>

      <h2 class="text-lg font-bold text-dark mt-8 mb-3">11. Governing law</h2>
      <p class="text-muted leading-relaxed">
        These terms are governed by the laws of the Province of Quebec, Canada. Disputes will be resolved
        in the courts of Montreal, Quebec.
      </p>

      <div class="mt-12 pt-6 border-t border-border">
        <p class="text-sm text-muted-light">
          Contact: <a href="mailto:wietze.suijker@gmail.com" class="text-primary hover:underline">wietze.suijker@gmail.com</a>
        </p>
      </div>
    </article>
  </main>
  <Footer />
</Base>
